casebody.data:
No. 697,

Misc.

Monge v. Smyth, Collector of Internal Revenue. Wareham C. Seaman for petitioner. Solicitor General Sobeloff, Assistant Attorney General Rice and Hilbert P. Zarky for respondent.

Appeal from and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit.

Per Curiam:

The appeal is dismissed for want of jurisdiction. The petition for writ of cer-tiorari is denied.
